    <div class="faq-item">
        <div class="question" onclick="toggleAnswer(this)">How can I book a turf?</div>
        <div class="answer">
            <p>To book a turf, follow these steps:</p>
            <ol>
                <li>Sign up or log in to your account.</li>
                <li>Search for available turfs based on your location and preferred date and time.</li>
                <li>Select a turf that suits your needs.</li>
                <li>Choose the desired booking duration i.e., date and time.</li>
                <li>Review your booking details and proceed to the payment page.</li>
                <li>Make the payment to confirm your booking.</li>
                <li>You will receive a confirmation email with your booking details.</li>
            </ol>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="faq-item">
        <div class="question" onclick="toggleAnswer(this)">What is host match? How it works?</div>
        <div class="answer">
            <ul>
                <li>
                    Host a match button simply creates a notification to all the public users that you are making a 
                challenge to match with your team at your desired location and time so when anyone's team
                is ready to take your challenge and accept it to match with your team.
                </li>
                <li>
                    Its a friendly match challenge with any team available at your time and your place. Here a turf
                is booked on the name of match hosting team.
                </li>
                <li>
                    ** Its a team match with 9x9 players and not an individual challenge**
                </li>
            </ul>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="faq-item">
        <div class="question" onclick="toggleAnswer(this)">How can I host a match?</div>
        <div class="answer">
            <p>To host a match, follow these steps:</p>
            <ol>
                <li>Sign up or log in to your account.</li>
                <li>Search for available matches based on your location and preferred date and time.</li>
                <li>Or click on 'Host a Match' button</li>
                <li>Select the date and turf that suits your needs.</li>
                <li>The available slots will only be shown if you select the turf</li>
                <li>Choose the desired booking time.</li>
                <li>Review your booking details and proceed to the payment page.</li>
                <li>Make the payment to confirm your booking.</li>
                <li>You will receive a confirmation email with your match details.</li>
                <li>When someone accepts your challenge you will get a notification on email (soon available on sms)</li>
            </ol>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="faq-item">
        <div class="question" onclick="toggleAnswer(this)">What if no one accepts your challenge?</div>
        <div class="answer">
            <ul>
                <li>
                    If no one accepts your challenge you can cancel the bookings 8 hrs before the game starts.
                    You will get your refund in terms of points to book your next turf. 
                </li>
                <li>
                    You can also play a practice match game with your localteam on booked turf.
                </li>
                <li>
                    For any assistance you cal call our customer care no: +91 9011786979.
                </li>
            </ul>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="faq-item">
