    <div class="faq-item">
        <div class="question" onclick="toggleAnswer(this)">Can I cancel or reschedule my booking?</div>
        <div class="answer">
            <p>Yes, you can cancel your booking. However, cancellation policies may vary
                depending on the turf provider. Please refer to the specific cancellation and rescheduling terms
                mentioned during the booking process or contact our support team for assistance.</p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="faq-item">
        <div class="question" onclick="toggleAnswer(this)">If I cancel, how do I get my refund?</div>
        <div class="answer">
            <p>When you cancel the booking a request is carried out to turf provider. When your booking is cancelled before
                8hrs of your scheduled time, we make sure that you get all your booked amount except 5% payment gateway charges.
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>

